com.codahale.metrics.ganglia

Class GangliaReporter.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codahale.metrics.ganglia.GangliaReporter.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    GangliaReporter

    public static class GangliaReporter.Builder
extends Object
    A builder for GangliaReporter instances. Defaults to using a tmax of 60, a dmax of 0, converting rates to events/second, converting durations to milliseconds, and not filtering metrics.
